Pre-Game Insights: Oman could emerge as the dark horses of the groups who could end up giving a tough fight to the well-established opponents.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Oman will begin its 2024T20 World Cup journey by taking on African side Namibia.
Oman will play against England, Australia, Scotland, and Namibia in the group stage.
Others: The squad is full of talent with former skipper Zeeshan Maqsood joining the team along with batting all-rounder Mohammed Nadeem.
